longBusinessSummary: Victory Battery Metals Corp., a junior exploration stage mining company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in Canada and the United States. It explores for lithium, nickel, gold, and copper. The company was formerly known as Victory Resources Corporation and changed its name to Victory Battery Metals Corp. in December 2022. Victory Battery Metals Corp. was incorporated in 1984 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
